des:
Hey! products help you easily control your home appliances. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your bulbs, plugs and other smart devices.

There's no need to go to the switch to adjust your lighting- just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
Connect Alexa to your Hey! products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “Hey!” app from the google play or app store;
(2). Register an account in our “Hey!” app;
(3). You need to have some devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Hey!” app and set appropriate names for your devices which will be used in Hey! skills;
(5). Download Amazon ""Alexa"" app from the google play, app store or Amazon app market.
(6). Configure Echo with ""Alexa"" app;
(7). Search “Hey!” skill from the ""Alexa"" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of “Hey!"", and you'll be navigated to Hey! login page;
(9). Input your Hey! account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
